data.description: A spectacular mountain view home in Rosena Ranch featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms  and a cozy loft for entertaining your friends and family. Upon entering the home, you  become captivated by its open floor plan and inviting family room. Plantation shutters  overlook a beautifully landscaped backyard filled with roses, a fig tree, and a draft orange   and tangerine tree. The kitchen is surrounded by beautifully upgraded tile floors and  granite countertops. A spacious area for family meals and a large pantry for all those  Costco visits only ten minutes away. Upstairs is your master bedroom with separate bath  and shower, as well as, a spacious walk-in closet. While upstairs you will also find two  additional bedrooms, a full bath, and a loft perfect for enjoying time together with your  loved ones watching tv and looking out at a magnificent mountain view. This home is in a  highly sought after Rosena Ranch Community which offers 2 pools, one being a Jr. Olympic pool,   a splash pad, clubhouse with a meeting room, 24 hr. state of the art fitness center with yoga  room, picnic and BBQ areas, a sports park with multi-sports fields, playgrounds and hiking trails,  all conveniently nestled in a peaceful hillside just North of the 210 off the 15 freeway. If a  turnkey home and a place to create beautiful memories is what you’re looking for, look no  further, this is the place of your dreams.
